<div class="story">  <p>Duck Ridge Shores is a ocean to sound subdivision located in Duck with 60 buildings lots situated on either side of Dune Road. There are no amenities other than the beach access which keeps the association fee down to a minimum. You can find Duck Ridge Shores just past <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/bayberry-bluffs.asp" title="Bayberry Bluff">Bayberry Bluff</a> as you head north on Rt 12 and just before you get to <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/duck/colony-by-the-sea.asp" title="Colony by the Sea">Colony by the Sea</a> condos. </p>
